Package: battery-mqtt-monitor
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash, upower, jq, mosquitto-clients, bc
Maintainer: battery-mqtt-monitor contributors
Description: Publishes battery status to MQTT for Home Assistant
 Monitors battery charge, status, time remaining, and wear level,
 then publishes them as JSON to an MQTT broker every minute.
 Compatible with Home Assistant MQTT Auto-Discovery.
